=== Public membership ===
{{anchor|CNRE – Résistance}}
'''{{lang|fr|CNRE – Résistance}}''' is a legal association created concurrently with the Council under the French law of 1901. Its purpose is to welcome natural persons and legal entities of French or foreign nationality, who wish to actively support the action of the CNRE, by relaying its ideas, through militant actions or through financial contributions.<ref name=":1" />

